    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being offered as a reliable daily driver. While the car runs and drives well, the exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear in the high-traffic areas, and some of the plastic trim has become brittle over time. Mechanically, it has been maintained, though it may soon require routine servicing for items like brake pads or tires. This is an honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
