    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute dream of a car. Seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty from day one, and it's in truly flawless shape inside and out. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here\u2014it still has that new car magic. It\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
