    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in flawless condition. This example features the F22C1 2.2L longitudinal DOHC VTEC inline-four, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains factory-spec with its signature X-bone frame and double-wishbone suspension geometry, providing exceptional torsional rigidity and turn-in response. All factory VIN tags are present on original body panels. Recent comprehensive service includes a valve clearance adjustment, fresh MTF-3 transmission fluid, and a brake system bleed. Zero modifications; a pristine, analog masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
